    <br>Jessie is a San Diego native. She has a love of the outdoors, the ocean, puppies, and authentic Mexican food. After graduating from Torrey Pines High School, she attended Oberlin College and Olin College of Engineering. Jessie currently works as a math and science tutor in Los Angeles. She also leads Premiere, a semi-pro all-female a cappella group, and spends her free time programming and arranging music.
