    <br>Jordan was born in New York but grew up in San Diego. After graduating from Torrey Pines High School, he studied music and physics at Oberlin College. He worked for two years, realized he did not have a passion for e-commerce, and decided to become a patent attorney. He is in his second year at UCLA School of Law. Jordan still loves to play the guitar and visits the beach as often as possible.
