    <td width="400"><b>Jessie's story:</b>
    <p>I played in the Jazz Band every year during high school. After my sophomore year, the group had a lot of turnover, and Jordan joined as our resident guitarist. We were instant best friends, having similar passions, work ethics, and a certain humor about life. It wasn't until one of my female friends asked me if he was "available," did I realize how much I actually liked him. Carefully walking the friendship line, I asked him to be my date to the Winter Formal dance, and, of course, he said "yes."</p>
    </td></tr></table>
 
